title: SanDisk is reportedly eager to sell itself off
text:
SanDisk is reportedly eager to sell itself off 
Published By: Tuaw.com - Today 
SanDisk is a mainstay of the storage world thanks to its memory cards and solid-state drives, but you might not see its name for much longer...
